## Verification gate (run by verifier agent)

> Use `;` (NOT `&&`) so a single failure does not hide later failures. Verifier collects ALL verdicts.

- [ ] `cd museum-backend; pnpm lint; pnpm test`
- [ ] `cd museum-frontend; npm run lint; npm test`
- [ ] `cd museum-web; pnpm lint; pnpm test` (if web touched)
- [ ] `gitnexus_detect_changes()` shows only expected scope
- [ ] no new `eslint-disable` without justification (Phase 0 hard rule)
- [ ] no inline test entities (factory shape-match passes — Phase 7)
- [ ] handoff briefs ≤ 200 tokens (`team-hooks/post-edit-lint.sh` enforces)
- [ ] STORY.md untouched on prior phases (`team-hooks/pre-complete-verify.sh` enforces via sha256 chain)
